{"tid":2512643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜濤壓力爆煲暈倒","createTime":"2021-05-02T01:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T03:03:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"39e6c09b5b16f32bafde3c773139bb285e399e0c","tid":2512643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210502/ZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210502%2FZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=6f16b304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210502%2FZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI%2F&h=de8a0a67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210502/ZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI/</a><br />\n<br />\n姜濤壓力爆煲暈倒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pB86jRmRQBjJWSt1SINf9Ox0xMc=/624x603/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQPE75YG55HT5HZ4WTDVFYY4KM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpB86jRmRQBjJWSt1SINf9Ox0xMc%3D%2F624x603%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQPE75YG55HT5HZ4WTDVFYY4KM.jpg&h=8e49d44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■姜濤昨日凌晨開直播，自言近日壓力大，情緒亦很差。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n人氣王姜濤前日22歲生日，「姜糖」花近百萬在銅鑼灣、中環及尖沙嘴等地大賣廣告祝壽，還有電車及巴士廣告，把他現居的銅鑼灣打造成「姜濤灣」。為答謝「姜糖」支持，姜B昨日凌晨1時在Ig開直播跟姜糖傾偈，高峯時有逾萬人收看，但他全程表現身心俱疲，除再三多謝姜糖的支持及送上的生日祝福外，他亦自爆近月來情緒極差：「呢段時間發生好多嘢，確實未消化得晒，攞到獎當然係好事，但同時壓力亦大咗好多，尤其呢排情緒好差，直到兩日前都成日發脾氣，希望之前因我發脾氣而影響到嘅人，講聲唔好意思。」其間姜B重提梅窩事件，再向fans道歉，另外談到好友猝死：「件事被傳媒寫咗出嚟，影響到佢嘅家人，唔好意思。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LT7oZQnoz__fiPbAT2rMrrl2ZAc=/624x936/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6O5HOFGCSFF6NEZJRW5UDLWQZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLT7oZQnoz__fiPbAT2rMrrl2ZAc%3D%2F624x936%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6O5HOFGCSFF6NEZJRW5UDLWQZI.jpg&h=baa42e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■姜濤近日為MIRROR今個月的九展騷進行密集式綵排。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向Candy致歉<br />\n<br />\n姜濤在直播時自爆日前排舞時暈倒：「我事後先知道，可能真係太眼瞓、太攰，有啲暈，加上全日冇乜食嘢。好白癡呀&hellip;&hellip;呢件事，咁我有食返嘢嘅，所以大家唔使擔心。」他透露演唱會後會放長假處理私事，不少姜糖叮囑他好好休息。尾聲時，姜濤亦有提到與「YOLO女」黃曦誼（Candy）傳緋聞：「真係一個誤會，新聞出街後睇到留言係咁鬧佢，想同佢講唔好意思。」昨日更有報道指，姜濤工作不絕，近半年內保守估計已吸金逾200萬，認真厲害。"},{"pid":"7e8a6279d7b61c928a18826e01243d61c496ac3a","tid":2512643,"uid":158337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa7fd36a9741a8c99d4409fa799b90069e556f8","tid":2512643,"uid":389865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9f107a17d8845b3e27524ccd96da01536a5ee5","tid":2512643,"uid":109679,"like":9,"dislike":41,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"咁辛苦咪唔好做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4679dfe516ef1e10113a11edf8c2090c38dea4c","tid":2512643,"uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"寧願開直播都唔合埋眼休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640c34930b0d5b015be053ae24c8bef3e3773683","tid":2512643,"uid":164240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"